title: 1961–62 Scottish Cup
text: The 1961–62 <a href="Scottish%20Cup">Scottish Cup</a> was the 77th staging of Scotland's most prestigious <a href="Association%20football">football</a> knockout competition. The Cup was won by <a href="Rangers%20F.C.">Rangers</a> who defeated <a href="St%20Mirren%20F.C.">St Mirren</a> in the final.
